{"vocabInfos":[{"lsjDefs":"<b> ἄργῠρος</b>, ὁ, <br /> (ἀργός A) <b>white metal,</b> i.e. <b>silver,</b> ἐξ Ἀλύβης ὅθεν ἀργύρου ἐστὶ γενέθλη[<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 8th c.BC: Ilias Homerus Epicus “Illiad” 2.857; so πηγὴ ἀργύρου 4th-5th c.BC: Aeschylus Tragicus “Persae” 238, etc.; ἄ. κοῖλος \">Refs 8th c.BC+</a>]<b>silver plate,</b> [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 4th c.BC: Theopompus Historicus 283a, 4th c.BC: Aristoteles Philosophus “Oeconomica” 1350b23, etc. \">Refs 4th c.BC+</a>]<br /><Level3><b>__2</b></Level3> ἄ. χυτός <b>quicksilver,</b> [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" [prev. author] “de An.” 406b19, “Mete.” 385b4, 4th-3rd c.BC: Theophrastus Philosophus “de Lapidibus” 60. \">Refs 4th c.BC+</a>]<br /><Level2><b>__II</b></Level2> ={ἀργύριον}, <b>silver-money,</b> generally, <b>money,</b> [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 4th-5th c.BC: Aeschylus Tragicus “Supplices” 935; ἐπ᾽ ἀργύρῳ γε τὴν ψυχὴν προδούς 5th c.BC: Sophocles Tragicus “Antigone” 322\">Refs 5th c.BC+</a>]; εἴ τι μὴ ξὺν ἀργύρῳ ἐπράσσετ᾽ by <b>bribery,</b> [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" [prev. author] “OT” 124\">Refs</a>]; in later Prose, coupled with χρυσός, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" NT.Matt.10.9, 4th c.AD: Alciphro Epistolographus 2.3. \">NT+4th c.AD+</a>]<br /><Level2><b>__III</b></Level2> ={λινόζωστος ἄρρην}, Ps.-[<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 1st c.AD: Dioscorides (Dioscurides) Medicus 4.189.\">Refs 1st c.AD+</a>]","strongNumber":"G0696","accentedUnicode":"ἄργυρος","relatedNos":[{"strongNumber":"G0693","matchingForm":"ἀργύρεος","stepTransliteration":"argureos","gloss":"silver","_zh_tw_Gloss":"銀","_es_Gloss":"de plata","_zh_Gloss":"银"},{"strongNumber":"G0694","matchingForm":"ἀργύριον","stepTransliteration":"argurion","gloss":"money","_zh_tw_Gloss":"銀子","_es_Gloss":"plata","_zh_Gloss":"银子"},{"strongNumber":"G0695","matchingForm":"ἀργυροκόπος","stepTransliteration":"argurokopos","gloss":"silversmith","_zh_tw_Gloss":"銀匠","_es_Gl